headline: What Is Shaping The Next Chapter In The Keysight Technologies (KEYS) Story Today
summary: Keysight Technologies just saw its modeled fair value edge up from US$220.00 to about US$220.69 as recent Street commentary absorbed better than expected earnings delivery, steady margins, and signs of demand stabilization. Analysts who raised their targets often cited fiscal Q4 EPS above consensus, guidance for fiscal Q1 EPS ahead of expectations, and early signs that wireless and defense demand may be firming. More cautious voices still referenced cyclicality and a steady 5% to 7% organic...
